nodes.text: Cairn's Flying Circus was a traveling circus that performed in the Minos Cluster. The circus included a foul-tempered Abyssin, two mutating aliens, three clowns, six Af'El lions and their trainer, a Kitonak band, and acrobat and her strong-man boyfriend, a Togorian knife-thrower, and the ringmaster. In reality, Cairn's Flying Circus was comprised of Alliance spies sent by No-Holds-Barred to search for Drun Cairnwick.
